TwitFrame

TwitFrame is an Android application that allows the user to view their Twitter stream as it flows in. This can be 
handy if you like docking your phone at your desk and want to use it for more than just a glorified clock. The 
application is in the Google Play store currently and is available at: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.MillerByteworks.TwitFrame&feature=nav_result#?t=W251bGwsMSwxLDMsImNvbS5NaWxsZXJCeXRld29ya3MuVHdpdEZyYW1lIl0.